OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777032715
OL,3,C'You need the belief to win' - Saints
OL,4,Cboss ahead of FA Cup semi-final at
OL,5,CWembley
OL,7,FSouthampton boss Tonda Eckert has said
OL,8,Fhis team have the belief they can win
OL,9,Fahead of their FA Cup semi-final
OL,10,Fagainst Manchester City at Wembley.
OL,12,FOn Saturday 35,750 Saints fans will
OL,13,Ftravel to the capital for the crucial
OL,14,Ftie.
OL,16,FSpeaking at a press conference on
OL,17,FThursday Eckert said: "You can feel
OL,18,Fthat around the club for, for many,
OL,19,Fmany weeks and months now that, this
OL,20,Fyear is very special.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777032715
OL,3,C'You need the belief to win' - Saints
OL,4,Cboss ahead of FA Cup semi-final at
OL,5,CWembley
OL,7,F"Competition itself obviously always
OL,8,Fspecial.
OL,10,F"But now with it being the 50th
OL,11,Fanniversary of the last time we've won
OL,12,Fit even more so, and there's no better
OL,13,Fway than to represent that than with
OL,14,Fthe shirt that we're wearing.
OL,16,F"If you don't go into games with the
OL,17,Fbelief that you are going to win then
OL,18,Fyou don't need to show up.
OL,20,F"And I think you find that belief very
OL,21,Fdeep inside.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777032715
OL,3,C'You need the belief to win' - Saints
OL,4,Cboss ahead of FA Cup semi-final at
OL,5,CWembley
OL,7,F"That's something that we transmit
OL,8,Fevery single day and I think that the
OL,9,Fplayers have that feeling and that's
OL,10,Fkey no matter who you come up against."
OL,12,F"It's a big stadium, obviously, but, I
OL,13,Fthink there's a big difference,"
OL,14,FEckert added.
OL,16,F"I don't go there for the experience.
OL,17,FI don't go there as a spectator. We go
OL,18,Fthere to challenge. And, I think
OL,19,Fthat's a very different way of
OL,20,Fapproaching."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777032715
OL,3,C'You need the belief to win' - Saints
OL,4,Cboss ahead of FA Cup semi-final at
OL,5,CWembley
OL,7,FSouthampton have only won the almighty
OL,8,Ftrophy once before, on May 1, 1976.
OL,10,FThe side defeated Manchester United 1-
OL,11,F0 to lift the cup.
OL,13,FEckert pointed to defending their box,
OL,14,Fsustained spells of possession and
OL,15,Fhurting City on the counter-attack as
OL,16,Fthree key areas that Saints must get
OL,17,Fright if they are to reach their first
OL,18,FFA Cup final since 2003, and stay on
OL,19,Fcourse to replicate the club's cup-
OL,20,Fwinning heroes of 1976, 50 years on.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777032715
OL,3,C'You need the belief to win' - Saints
OL,4,Cboss ahead of FA Cup semi-final at
OL,5,CWembley
OL,7,F"It's the same as we've needed against
OL,8,Fmany teams that we've come up against
OL,9,Fover the last weeks," he said.
OL,11,F"You will have some periods where you
OL,12,Fneed to suffer and accept that you may
OL,13,Fnot touch the ball for a minute, and
OL,14,Fjust stay calm in those moments.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777032715
OL,3,C'You need the belief to win' - Saints
OL,4,Cboss ahead of FA Cup semi-final at
OL,5,CWembley
OL,7,F"If you see where City score their
OL,8,Fgoals, I think most of them are within
OL,9,Fthe width of the six-yard box and most
OL,10,Fof them are inside the 18-yard box, so
OL,11,Fthere might be some moments where you
OL,12,Fjust need to defend inside your box
OL,13,Fand be very clear on how to do that.
OL,15,F"On the other hand I think there are
OL,16,Fmore than enough chances ` we're
OL,17,Fdefinitely going to have a couple of
OL,18,Ftransition moments and we need to be
OL,19,Fcrucial on the ones that they give to
OL,20,Fus, because it's not going to be too
OL,21,Fmany.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777032715
OL,3,C'You need the belief to win' - Saints
OL,4,Cboss ahead of FA Cup semi-final at
OL,5,CWembley
OL,7,F"At the same time you can't rely only
OL,8,Fon defending in these games, so we
OL,9,Fneed to be brave enough and find
OL,10,Fanother gear, and the energy so that
OL,11,Fwhen we do have the ball, we have
OL,12,Fspells in possession.
OL,14,F"I think we have found quite a good
OL,15,Fcombination of both of these aspects
OL,16,Fagainst Arsenal, and they will be the
OL,17,Fkey again on Saturday."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
